{"tid":2390834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《香港志》耗$7.8億貶港英貢獻偏袒中共　史學者批「爛書」歪曲不實","createTime":"2021-02-01T23:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T01:35:58.000Z","uid":271829,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b413f874c8f1759ec459d7f38086dcb720335743","tid":2390834,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yrqOBd2Jg27kbtuygV4GwKPWTok=/2480x2480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CYHZT2QQBNFGPDA3ONAULAWLPE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyrqOBd2Jg27kbtuygV4GwKPWTok%3D%2F2480x2480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCYHZT2QQBNFGPDA3ONAULAWLPE.png&h=b6570dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vk2VQtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVk2VQtE.jpg&h=91b05dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n淡化共產黨缺失<br />\n總述部份第21頁，有關「二戰後移民與經濟發展」條目，亦被程翔指出失實之處。有關條目稱「二戰之後在國共內戰和政權更迭的衝擊下，大量合法和非法移民到港」，但條目形容背後原因為「其後政治環境轉變，他們再難返回內地」。程翔批評《香港志》刻意隱藏移民潮背後真正原因，當時正值土地改革運動、鎮壓反革命運動等，「大陸嘅人係逃避共產主義災難而走嚟香港，就唔係一般移民」。<br />\n淡化共產黨或親共團體錯失，在此書例子不少。程翔指同樣在總述部份，第30頁有關「社會矛盾的激化與社會動亂」中，六七暴動緣起的描述為「社會固有矛盾，加上文革極左思潮影響」，而條目中擺放炸彈者僅稱「左派」，亦無有關工聯會的敍述。<br />\n反觀1956年九龍及荃灣暴動，書中就稱「導火線帶有明顯的政治色彩，親國民黨工會和與其有關的黑社會組織的挑動及參與顯而易見」，此等描述有其指向性，「1967年個暴動係文化大革命（從中國）延伸嚟香港，無政治色彩咩？」記者同樣翻查2016年魚蛋革命條目字眼，發現書中第674頁圖364的相片描述，形容「暴徒於旺角暴亂中跳上被砸毀的士的車頂」，與描述參加六七暴動的「左派」大有分別。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/PIAEB2MAOZEQVGKYNKLTGGHDWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FPIAEB2MAOZEQVGKYNKLTGGHDWQ%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=f0d68286\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210202%2FPIAEB2MAOZEQVGKYNKLTGGHDWQ%2F&h=072c1b6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210202/PIAEB2MAOZEQVGKYNKLTGGHDWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"f16db174d098d901a054cf8e421a481d98b1d825","tid":2390834,"uid":55089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:52:07.000Z","msg":"虫泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53395daf273f01bcef285ab370a25e2a2a9be8a","tid":2390834,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:53:01.000Z","msg":"熱狗又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b168a5404c2bb35c67bc32329dadf22d974f1a4","tid":2390834,"uid":284855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:55:07.000Z","msg":"未來中史科目應該會以依本垃圾做藍本"},{"pid":"7e1bed4279ff0ea3f48f309664483b8d0c6365d0","tid":2390834,"uid":13503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:57:07.000Z","msg":"拎黎抆屎都怕戒到屎眼"},{"pid":"f8a33e6dd17bdd89f97f60b99ca2bbbaa4deaa31","tid":2390834,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"下， 熱狗出㗎？！"},{"pid":"acb24d2e774c14b612a5db7f6b3a8e614ee0ff53","tid":2390834,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:58:46.000Z","msg":"丁新豹呢條奶共撚屌改名丁蟹啦"},{"pid":"b164a253ec5187f54d21972db93e962153166800","tid":2390834,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8a33e6dd17bdd89f97f60b99ca2bbbaa4deaa31","tid":2390834,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"下， 熱狗出㗎？！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T00:01:07.000Z","msg":"蟲太認證呢本「屎」詩式大作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"